Sentencas: The conventional oxygen electrode degrades when operated in reversible solid oxide fuel cell (RSOFC) mode.
Titulo: Investigation on SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 double perovskite as an oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: To address this issue, double perovskites have been explored as promising cathode electrodes in RSOFC with proton conducting electrolyte as the electrolyte.
Titulo: Investigation on SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 double perovskite as an oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In the present study, SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 (SBSCF) double perovskite is explored as the oxygen electrode using YSZ as the electrolyte.
Titulo: Investigation on SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 double perovskite as an oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The SBSCF has been successfully synthesized using a simple and cost-effective solution combustion technique as the oxygen electrode for RSOFC.
Titulo: Investigation on SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 double perovskite as an oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The structural, morphological and electrical conductivity of SBSCF powder and the electrochemical performance of SOFC containing SBSCF as cathode material are discussed.
Titulo: Investigation on SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 double perovskite as an oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance of the cell in the electrolyzer mode is also discussed.
Titulo: Investigation on SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+8 double perovskite as an oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide fuel cell
